YOU SOMEWHERE,

31:14.830 --> 31:16.092
AWAY FROM ALL THIS.

31:16.100 --> 31:17.021
NO.

31:17.030 --> 31:18.327
THEY'RE ADULTS.

31:18.330 --> 31:21.299
