TO COSTA RICA,

31:24.560 --> 31:26.050
A WEEK FROM MONDAY.

31:26.060 --> 31:27.527
SEPARATE ROOMS.

31:30.330 --> 31:32.855
I WAS 19 WHEN
I GOT MARRIED.

31:32.860 --> 31:35.397
I'VE NEVER BEEN
ON MY OWN.

31:35.400 --> 31:38.153
I WOULDN'T
EVEN KNOW HOW.

31:42.160 --> 31:43.855
I'M SORRY.

31:46.300 --> 31:49.019
YOU'RE A VERY
KIND PERSON, AND,

31:49.030 --> 31:50.918
