31:53.800 --> 31:55.495
I'M SORRY.

31:59.700 --> 32:00.758
GOODBYE.

32:11.560 --> 32:21.151
( country rock playing )

32:21.160 --> 32:24.095
GOOD CHOICE
OF MUSIC.

32:24.100 --> 32:26.728
