ALL FROM HER.

32:39.860 --> 32:41.498
NOW SHE'S BROKE
WITH A BABY,

32:41.500 --> 32:42.797
AND YOU'RE GONNA
LEAVE HER ALONE.

32:42.800 --> 32:44.358
WHO THE FUCK
ARE YOU ?!

32:44.360 --> 32:46.419
I OWN THIS PLACE,
GET THE HELL OUT
BEFORE I CALL THE COPS.

32:46.430 --> 32:47.795
YOU PEOPLE SUCK.

32:48.700 --> 32:49.997
( door slamming )

32:50.000 --> 32:52.059
WHAT WAS THAT ?

32:52.060 --> 32:54.620
