OWED MONEY TO.

32:59.060 --> 33:02.552
NATE, I NOTICE
MR. SWANSON IS IN
THE TITAN CASKET.

33:02.560 --> 33:04.755
YEAH, YEAH, BUT
SHE'S GIVING IT BACK.

33:04.760 --> 33:06.523
