FOR CREMATION.

33:06.530 --> 33:09.499
THEY CAN'T GIVE IT BACK,
BY LAW, IT HAS TO BE
BURNED WITH HIM.

33:09.500 --> 33:11.695
YOU JUST COST US $9,000,
YOU FUCKING MORON.

33:11.700 --> 33:12.826
WHAT ?

33:12.830 --> 33:14.252
( doorbell )

33:14.260 --> 33:16.649
HOW WAS I SUPPOSED
TO KNOW THAT ?

33:21.060 --> 33:23.620
I'M SO SORRY
ABOUT YOUR FATHER.

33:23.630 --> 33:25.188
JENNIFER.

33:29.500 --> 33:31.650
I WAS IN BOCA RATON.

33:31.660 --> 33:33.719
MY MOM HAD TO HAVE
HER HIP REPLACED.

33:33.730 --> 33:35.049
OH, DEAR,
HOW IS SHE ?

33:35.060 --> 33:36.618
SHE'S BETTER,
THAN KS.

33:36.630 --> 33:38.825
SO, I DIDN'T FIND OUT
ABOUT MR. FISHER

33:38.830 --> 33:40.354
'TIL YESTERDAY.

33:40.360 --> 33:42.954
I'M JUST
HEARTBROKEN
ABOUT IT.

33:42.960 --> 33:44.655
I'LL MISS HIM.

33:44.660 --> 33:46.218
WELL,
HE ADORED YOU.

33:49.730 --> 33:51.789
OH, DAVID,

33:51.800 --> 33:54.997
I WON'T BE ANSWERING
THE PHONES ANYMORE.

33:57.430 --> 33:59.227
UH, OKAY.

34:09.960 --> 34:12.190
NOW EVERY PART
OF YOUR BODY

34:12.200 --> 34:13.849
HAS A NEW
MEANING TO ME.

34:15.360 --> 34:17.396
WE SHOULD GO.

34:17.400 --> 34:19.994
LIKE YOUR NOSE.

34:20.000 --> 34:21.228
C'MON.

34:21.230 --> 34:23.551
AND YOUR
LITTLE HANDS.

34:23.560 --> 34:25.323
HANDS I GET.

34:25.330 --> 34:28.822
AND YOUR TOES.

34:28.830 --> 34:30.991
IT'S TICKLISH.

34:31.000 --> 34:32.456
HERE, TRY THESE.

34:32.460 --> 34:34.291
YOU CAN
PLAY WITH MINE.

34:34.300 --> 34:37.394
YOU'RE RIGHT, NOW
I DON'T FEEL ANYTHING.

34:37.400 --> 34:39.197
SEE, IT'S PERFECT.

34:42.100 --> 34:43.954
WOULD YOU, UM...

34:47.100 --> 34:49.489
NAH, I'M EMBARRASSED.

34:49.500 --> 34:50.421
WHAT ?

34:53.460 --> 34:56.327
WOULD YOU RUB IT ?

34:59.600 --> 35:00.749
OKAY.

35:02.760 --> 35:05.228
