MY TOE HARD.

35:08.630 --> 35:11.349
DO YOU WANT
TO KISS IT ?

35:11.360 --> 35:12.759
YOUR TOE ?

35:12.760 --> 35:13.988
NO.

35:14.000 --> 35:16.093
C'MON, I'LL DO
SOMETHING FOR YOU.

35:16.100 --> 35:17.021
ANYTHING.

35:20.430 --> 35:23.399
AREN'T YOU
FORGETTING SOMETHING ?

35:24.530 --> 35:25.952
OH.

35:27.330 --> 35:28.558
PLEASE.

35:40.330 --> 35:43.857
UGH, YOU FILTHY,
DEAD FUCK.

35:49.300 --> 35:51.552
HEY, NATE.

35:51.560 --> 35:52.891
KEITH.

35:52.900 --> 35:54.891
