YOUR DAD'S VIEWING.

35:54.900 --> 35:56.925
OH, YEAH, DAVID'S
RACQUETBALL PARTNER.

35:56.930 --> 35:59.922
YEAH, IS, UH,
DAVID INSIDE ?

35:59.930 --> 36:03.559
NO, HE WENT OUT FOR DINNER
WITH HIS EX FIANCE.

36:03.560 --> 36:06.723
SHE MISSED DAD'S FUNERAL,
AND THEY WERE PRETTY CLOSE.

36:06.730 --> 36:09.528
HEY, THAT'S COOL,
I UNDERSTAND COMPLETELY.

36:09.530 --> 36:11.418
I HAVE HIS CELL PHONE NUMBER
IF YOU WANNA GIVE HIM A CALL.

36:11.430 --> 36:13.557
I ALREADY GAVE IT A SHOT,
HE DIDN'T ANSWER.

36:13.560 --> 36:16.028
HEY, IS DAVID
ANY GOOD,

36:16.030 --> 36:18.521
AT RACQUETBALL,
'CAUSE,

36:18.530 --> 36:20.327
WE USED TO PLAY WHEN
I WAS IN HIGH SCHOOL

36:20.330 --> 36:22.321
AND HE WAS PATHETIC,
RUNNIN' INTO WALLS.

36:22.330 --> 36:24.389
YEAH, I THINK YOU'D
BE PRETTY SURPRISED

36:24.400 --> 36:26.356
JUST HOW GOOD
HE'S GOTTEN.

36:26.360 --> 36:28.658
WELL, I'LL TELL HIM
YOU CAME BY.

36:28.660 --> 36:30.093
THAN KS.

36:40.530 --> 36:42.521
DEAR GOD.

36:50.030 --> 36:52.453
I NEED TO
GET HIS WATCH.

36:52.460 --> 36:55.099
I NEED TO SELL IT
FOR THE MONEY.

36:57.300 --> 36:59.723
MY LIFE IS OVER.

36:59.730 --> 37:01.789
THIS IS A HARD TIME,
THE HARDEST.

37:01.800 --> 37:04.018
IT WAS ALL A LIE.

37:04.030 --> 37:05.554
HE LEI-T US
WITH NOTHING

37:05.560 --> 37:07.528
BECAUSE THERE
NEVER WAS ANYTHING.

37:11.660 --> 37:13.093
BASTARD !

37:20.600 --> 37:22.795
( door closing )

37:32.660 --> 37:35.652
I ALMOST DIED WHEN I SAW
OUR ENGAGEMENT PICTURES

37:35.660 --> 37:37.457
STILL ON
YOUR MANTLE.

37:37.460 --> 37:38.893
WHY ?

37:38.900 --> 37:41.858
MY FAMILY LOVED YOU,
MY FATHER ESPECIALLY.

37:41.860 --> 37:44.294
HE LOVED YOU.

37:44.300 --> 37:47.224
HE HAD A FUNNY
WAY OF SHOWING IT.

37:51.600 --> 37:53.693
I'M DRUNK.

37:54.700 --> 37:56.622
THEN I CAN ASK.

37:57.560 --> 37:59.755
ARE YOU HAPPY ?

38:01.000 --> 38:03.025
I'M STILL ME.

38:06.500 --> 38:08.957
YOUR FATHER KNEW.

38:09.860 --> 38:12.055
WE HAD COFFEE ONCE
AND HE TOLD ME

38:12.060 --> 38:14.699
HE UNDERSTOOD WHY
WE COULDN'T BE TOGETHER.

38:14.700 --> 38:16.520
HE SAID YOU SPENT
SO MUCH TIME

38:16.530 --> 38:18.498
TRYING TO MAKE
OTHER PEOPLE HAPPY,

38:18.500 --> 38:21.219
YOU NEVER THOUGHT
ABOUT YOURSELF.

38:21.230 --> 38:23.926
HE WORRIED
ABOUT THAT.

38:26.600 --> 38:30.058
SO, DO YOU HAVE
ANYONE NOW ?

38:34.060 --> 38:36.449
CAN YOU TELL
ME ABOUT HIM ?

38:36.460 --> 38:38.894
YOU'RE COMPLETELY WRONG
ABOUT MY FATHER.

38:38.900 --> 38:41.357
YOU DIDN'T
KNOW HIM AT ALL,
NOBODY DID.

38:46.630 --> 38:49.622
LET'S GET A ROOM
AND FUCK OUR BRAINS OUT,

38:49.630 --> 38:51.120
HOW ABOUT IT ?

38:51.130 --> 38:53.348
JESUS, DAVID.

39:03.730 --> 39:05.095
HI.

39:05.100 --> 39:07.751
I GOT YOUR MESSAGE,
SORRY I DIDN'T CALL YOU BACK.

39:07.760 --> 39:09.728
I HAD TO GO OUT
TO COUNTY HOSPITAL.

39:09.730 --> 39:12.096
THE BODY'S STILL
IN LONG BEACH.

39:12.100 --> 39:14.125
THE AUTOPSY'S
NOT EVEN FINISHED YET.

39:14.130 --> 39:15.893
IT'S UNBELIEVABLE.

39:15.900 --> 39:17.959
HOW WAS
THE MEETING ?

39:19.030 --> 39:20.691
EVERYONE ASKED
ABOUT YOU.

39:20.700 --> 39:22.588
THEY WANNA MEET YOU.

39:22.600 --> 39:24.750
I WANNA MEET THEM.

39:26.700 --> 39:28.827
I'M A LITTLE DRUNK,

39:28.830 --> 39:31.094
YOU MIGHT HAVE TO
UNDRESS ME.

39:31.100 --> 39:32.590
OKAY.

39:33.830 --> 39:36.128
RIGHT AFTER YOU
STOP LYING TO ME.

40:40.330 --> 40:42.127
UHH, BRENDA ?

40:42.130 --> 40:43.893
YES, NATE.

40:43.900 --> 40:46.949
WHY IS MY NAME
TATTOOED ON
YOUR ASS ?

40:46.960 --> 40:49.258
IT'S NOT YOUR NAME.

40:50.360 --> 40:52.521
YES, IT IS.

40:53.730 --> 40:56.449
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY
PERSON NAMED THAT.

41:05.600 --> 41:07.955
NATE, IT'S
A COINCIDENCE.

41:07.960 --> 41:09.723
IT'S NOT YOU
OR ANYONE YOU KNOW.

41:12.230 --> 41:14.949
C'MON, WHAT, YOU THINK
I'M SO ENAMORED WITH YOU

41:14.960 --> 41:17.690
I HAD YOUR NAME
BURNED INTO MY FLESH ?

41:17.700 --> 41:19.588
HOW COME I NEVER
SAW IT BEFORE ?

41:19.600 --> 41:22.091
WE'VE HAD SEX TWICE.

41:22.100 --> 41:25.228
ONCE WITH
OUR CLOTHES ON,

41:25.230 --> 41:28.449
AND ONCE IN THE DARK AFTER
THREE MARTINIS A PIECE.

41:28.460 --> 41:30.155
YOU OBVIOUSLY LIKED
SOME GUY ENOUGH

41:30.160 --> 41:31.718
TO HAVE HIS NAME
BURNED INTO YOUR FLESH.

41:35.160 --> 41:38.357
I WOULD HAVE DONE A LOT
MORE THAN THAT FOR HIM.

41:59.330 --> 42:03.619
( snoring )

42:21.400 --> 42:24.426
IT'S ABOUT TIME,
YOU FUCKING MORON.

42:24.430 --> 42:26.694
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING IN THERE ?

42:26.700 --> 42:29.021
COULD YOU HELP ME OUT,
YOU FUCKING MORON ?

42:29.030 --> 42:30.827
WHY CAN'T YOU
JUST CLIMB OUT ?

42:30.830 --> 42:34.095
I THINK WE BOTH KNOW
THE ANSWER TO THAT,
YOU FUCKING MORON.

42:45.300 --> 42:48.497
YOU REALLY SHOULD DO
SOMETHING ABOUT THIS.

42:48.500 --> 42:51.219
IT'S REALLY DEEP.

42:51.230 --> 42:54.154
MIGHT AS WELL
BE BLEEDING.

42:56.100 --> 42:58.751
COULD YOU BE A LITTLE
MORE DRAMATIC ?

42:58.760 --> 43:01.422
OH, I COULD BE
A LOT MORE DRAMATIC.

43:01.660 --> 43:04.549
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING TODAY ?

43:04.560 --> 43:08.496
DAVE AND I HAVE TO GO
GET THE REGISTRATION

43:08.500 --> 43:10.627
OUT OF THE WRECKED HEARSE.

43:10.630 --> 43:14.054
INSURANCE WON'T
REPLACE WITHOUT IT.

43:15.130 --> 43:16.495
WHAT TIME ?

43:16.500 --> 43:18.889
2:30, I THINK.

43:18.900 --> 43:21.095
TAKE YOUR
CELL PHONE.

43:21.100 --> 43:23.022
OKAY.

43:23.030 --> 43:25.225
PROMISE ME
YOU WILL.

43:26.030 --> 43:27.588
ALRIGHT.

43:37.030 --> 43:39.999
OH, I DON'T FEEL LIKE
CARBS THIS MORNING.

43:40.000 --> 43:43.254
DO WE HAVE ANYMORE OF THOSE
STEVIE NICKS RASPBERRIES ?

43:43.260 --> 43:44.989
CLAIRE.

43:45.000 --> 43:47.628
DO YOU HAVE AN
EATING DISORDER ?

43:47.630 --> 43:51.396
WHAT ? NO, MOM,
I WISH, BUT...

44:03.300 --> 44:05.450
ARE YOU
BEING HELPED ?

44:05.460 --> 44:07.451
YEAH...
MY POP'S HERE.

44:07.460 --> 44:08.597
SAU REZ.

44:08.600 --> 44:09.794
OF COURSE.

44:09.800 --> 44:12.223
THAT'S THE
TITAN SERIES.

44:12.230 --> 44:13.754
IT'S QUITE
BEAUTIFUL.

44:13.760 --> 44:14.988
GIVE ME A NUMBER.

44:15.000 --> 44:16.592
$9,000.

44:16.600 --> 44:19.455
YOU GUYS OUGHTA
GET YOUR ACT TOGETHER.

44:19.460 --> 44:21.599
YOUR BROTHER SAID
THAT THIS WAS ON SPECIAL,

44:21.600 --> 44:23.989
$4,500, AND THEN HE
CAME DOWN TO $4,000.

44:24.000 --> 44:25.854
SO, WHY DON'T
WE START THERE ?

44:29.200 --> 44:31.452
( Rico )
THAT'S NOT LEGAL,
RESELLING A COFFIN.

44:31.460 --> 44:33.325
THERE ARE FLUIDS
THAT SEEP.

44:33.330 --> 44:35.389
OKAY, AND
MR. SWANSON,
HE SEEPED.

44:35.400 --> 44:37.391
WHAT DID YOU
TELL MR. SAUREZ ?

44:37.400 --> 44:38.753
HEY, HE WANTS
A QUALITY COFFIN,

44:38.760 --> 44:40.227
WE HAPPEN TO HAVE
ONE AVAILABLE.

44:40.230 --> 44:41.595
I DON'T AGREE
WITH THIS AT ALL.

44:41.600 --> 44:43.454
IT'S AGAINST
MY BELIEFS.

44:43.460 --> 44:44.552
THANK YOU,
FEDERICO.

44:44.560 --> 44:45.629
AND IT'S
UNSANITARY.

44:45.630 --> 44:46.858
THEY'RE DEAD !

44:46.860 --> 44:48.396
WHAT DISEASE CAN
THEY POSSIBLY CATCH ?!

44:48.400 --> 44:50.891
IT'S TOO LATE, NATE,
IT'S A $9,000 RETAIL ITEM,

44:50.900 --> 44:52.856
OUR COST IS $3,200,
WE EAT THAT,

44:52.860 --> 44:54.498
PLUS WE LOSE
THE PROFIT.

44:54.500 --> 44:56.923
THERE'S A
$6,000 MARK UP ?!

45:02.930 --> 45:05.455
MR. SAUREZ, WE CANNOT
LET YOU HAVE THAT CASKET.

45:05.460 --> 45:07.257
I'M SORRY
TO HEAR THAT.

45:07.260 --> 45:09.296
WE CAN'T
LEGALLY SELL IT
TO YOU BECAUSE,

45:09.300 --> 45:11.894
VERY BRIEFLY, IT WAS
OCCUPIED BY ANOTHER PERSON.

45:11.900 --> 45:12.992
$3,500.

45:13.000 --> 45:13.898
SOLD !

45:13.900 --> 45:15.026
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

45:15.030 --> 45:16.452
DAVID, DON'T BE
A FUCKIN' MORON.

45:16.460 --> 45:18.519
LOOK, FELLAS, LET'S
SPLIT THE DIFFERENCE.

45:18.530 --> 45:21.021
BECAUSE I GOTTA GET
A HAIRCUT BEFORE THE SERVICE.

45:21.030 --> 45:22.622
MY BROTHER HAS
NO AUTHORIZATION--

45:22.630 --> 45:24.928
MR. SAUREZ,
IT'S A $9,000 PRODUCT,

45:24.930 --> 45:26.249
IT'S USED ONE NIGHT,

45:26.260 --> 45:27.818
YOU'RE GETTING IT
AT COST TO US.

45:27.830 --> 45:29.718
WOULD YOU BE
WILLING TO STIPULATE

45:29.730 --> 45:31.618
THAT YOU UNDERSTAND
THE CONDITION OF THE COFFIN ?

45:31.630 --> 45:32.927
SURE, WHATEVER.

45:32.930 --> 45:34.727
MAY I MAKE
A SUGGESTION ?

45:34.730 --> 45:36.652
YOU'VE CLOSED, OKAY ?

45:36.660 --> 45:39.595
DON'T OVER-CLOSE,
IT KILLS THE WORD OF MOUTH.

45:45.430 --> 45:55.192
( rock music playing )

46:06.160 --> 46:08.321
IS THAT THE BEST ANYBODY
COULD COME UP WITH ?

46:08.330 --> 46:10.252
"FATHER, HUSBAND,
CAREGIVER" ?

46:10.260 --> 46:12.148
HOW WOULD YOU PREFER ?

46:12.160 --> 46:14.355
INTROVERT, SADIST,
MIND-FUCKER ?

46:14.360 --> 46:16.453
( Gilardi )
EXCUSE ME,
MR. FISHER ?

46:16.460 --> 46:17.859
MATT GILARDI.

46:17.860 --> 46:19.748
KRONER SERVICE
INTERNATIONAL ?

46:19.760 --> 46:22.649
I UNDERSTAND YOU'RE NOW
PART OWNER OF THE BUSINESS.

46:24.200 --> 46:27.829
YOU ARE AWARE WE'VE MADE
A VERY RICH BUY-OUT OFFER
FOR YOUR UNIT.

46:27.830 --> 46:30.094
OKAY.

46:30.100 --> 46:32.819
THIS A ONE-TIME OFFER.

46:32.830 --> 46:34.650
I DON'T KNOW
ABOUT THAT.

46:34.660 --> 46:36.127
YOU THINK YOU
CAN HOLD OUT ?

46:36.130 --> 46:38.428
WE CONTROL
SUPPLIERS NOW.

46:38.430 --> 46:40.193
WHERE ARE YOU GONNA
GET YOUR CHEMICALS ?

46:40.200 --> 46:42.156
HOW 'BOUT YOUR
CASKETS AND LINERS ?

46:42.160 --> 46:43.696
WHAT ABOUT
THIS DIAZ KID ?

46:43.700 --> 46:46.021
I MEAN, THIS GUY
IS A TOP NOTCH
RESTORATIVE ARTIST.

46:46.030 --> 46:49.124
ARE YOU THREATENING TO
PUT US OUT OF BUSINESS ?

46:49.130 --> 46:51.052
WE LOOK AT IT
AS A PARTNERSHIP.

46:51.060 --> 46:52.652
IN THE DEATH CARE
INDUSTRY NOW,

46:52.660 --> 46:54.890
IT'S CONSOLIDATE OR DIE.

46:54.900 --> 46:57.926
DECIDE WHICH, NATE,
AND GIVE ME A RING.

46:57.930 --> 47:00.148
'CAUSE WE WILL PUT
THINGS IN MOTION,

47:00.160 --> 47:01.923
EITHER WAY.

47:06.130 --> 47:08.792
