IN MOTION EITHER WAY" ?

47:08.800 --> 47:10.199
WHOO-HOO
TOUGH GUY.

47:10.200 --> 47:11.519
SHUT UP.

47:14.030 --> 47:15.759
( attendant )
RIGHT IN HERE.

47:15.760 --> 47:17.751
SIGN THIS
RIGHT HERE.

47:32.000 --> 47:33.649
WELL, IT'S TOTALED.

47:33.660 --> 47:36.254
THE INSURANCE COMPANY
WAS RIGHT ABOUT THAT.

47:45.400 --> 47:47.288
WHOA, FUCK !

47:51.030 --> 47:52.918
THERE'S STILL
BLOOD ON THE WHEEL.

48:05.500 --> 48:08.151
OKAY, LET'S GO.

48:08.160 --> 48:10.549
JESUS, DON'T YOU
FEEL ANYTHING ?

48:11.830 --> 48:13.650
YEAH, I FEEL
BETRAYED.

48:14.830 --> 48:16.491
( phone )

48:18.660 --> 48:20.321
HELLO.

48:20.330 --> 48:23.219
( Brenda )
Meet me at the corner
of Sunset and Gordon.

48:23.230 --> 48:25.425
Now, it's
important.

48:25.430 --> 48:27.853
WHAT ?

48:27.860 --> 48:29.191
Bring your brother.

48:29.200 --> 48:31.156
Trust me,
you need to do this.

48:38.100 --> 48:40.250
I SPOKE
TO GILARDI.

48:40.260 --> 48:41.898
AND ?

48:41.900 --> 48:44.755
HE SAYS WE SELL OR THEY
PUT US OUT OF BUSINESS.

48:45.960 --> 48:47.120
FUCK.

48:49.900 --> 48:52.255
I THINK
WE SHOULD SELL.

48:52.260 --> 48:55.889
AND ERASE EVERYTHING THIS FAMILY
HAS MEANT FOR 50 YEARS ?

48:55.900 --> 48:58.619
THAT MIGHT NOT
BE A BAD THING.

49:08.730 --> 49:10.152
HEY.

49:10.160 --> 49:11.718
BRENDA.

49:11.730 --> 49:14.255
THIS IS
MY BROTHER, DAVE.

49:14.260 --> 49:15.522
C'MON.

49:17.630 --> 49:19.996
C'MON,
LET'S DO THIS.

49:30.130 --> 49:32.598
THIS IS
THE BUS.

49:32.600 --> 49:34.522
WHAT BUS ?

49:34.530 --> 49:36.657
THE BUS.

49:41.100 --> 49:42.795
BRENDA, THIS
ISN'T FUNNY.

49:42.800 --> 49:45.189
THIS IS
FUCKED UP.

49:45.200 --> 49:47.418
WHAT GIVES YOU THE RIGHT
TO DO SOMETHING LIKE THIS ?

